"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; display: block; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; }\nfigcaption.thlex-caption { font-size: 0.85em; color: #555; font-style: italic; margin-top: 0.2em; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"REALIA:1.3.1.3\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">1.3.1.3</span> 标题：网、陷阱网（net, trammel net）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">经文出处</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מָצוֹד</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：matsod（另参)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:6\">JOB 19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:26\">ECC 7:26</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">来：מְצוֹדָה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：mtsodah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:12\">ECC 9:12</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：δίκτυον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音译：diktuon)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:20\">MAT 4:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21\">MAT 4:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:18\">MRK 1:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19\">MRK 1:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:2\">LUK 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:4\">LUK 5:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:5\">LUK 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:6\">LUK 5:6</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">描述</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>\n            <figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0336_trammel_net.png\" alt=\"在束缚网里的鱼\"><figcaption class=\"thlex-caption\">在束缚网里的鱼 (Lindsay G. Thompson, University of Washington, CC0, via Wikimedia Commons)</figcaption></figure>陷阱网由两层或三层网组成，通常是中间一张网眼较小的内网，夹在两张网眼较大的外网中间。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">用途</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>与拖网相似，陷阱网垂直放入水中，通过浮在水面上的浮子和底部带有重物的绳索来固定位置。鱼会通过外网游到里面较细的内网（1），然后推着内网穿过另一侧的外网（2），这样鱼就被卡在网袋里面退不回去了（3）。拖网在张开之后会马上收网；然而陷阱网不一样，需要撒在水中几个小时，等待鱼卡在网袋里面。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻译</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>希伯来文<em>matsod</em> 和<em>mtsodah</em> 可能泛指“网”，包括渔网和打猎用的网。</p>\n<p>在<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:20\">MAT 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt4:21\">MAT 4:21</a> 、<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:18\">MRK 1:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark1:19\">MRK 1:19</a> 和<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:2\">LUK 5:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:4\">LUK 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:5\">LUK 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:6\">LUK 5:6</a> 中，希腊文<em>diktuon</em> 可能指的是拖网（<a class=\"thlex-xref\" data-bnType=\"lexiconLink\" data-collection=\"\" data-key=\"\" href=\"#\">1.3.1.2 拖网、围网 (dragnet, seine)&lt;REALIA:1.3.1.2&gt;</a> ），不过这个词的复数形式又表明它很可能是指陷阱网，因为陷阱网是由多层网组成的。如果目标语言不要求区分各种网，翻译者可以使用“网”的统称。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
